reviews.text:
The pineapple buns at Sai Kung Bakery are, hands down, no competition, THE BEST pineapple buns in all of Hong Kong. Because of the high turn over, the buns are always warm and fresh out of the oven. The top is always perfectly golden brown and crispy. The bun below is light, airy, and buttery. The line is generally very long, but it moves very quickly. I don't think I've ever spent more than 15 minutes in line. 

If you want to sit to enjoy your baked goods, it requires that you order a drink. You also have to wait for your own table as there is no seating service. I would say their drinks were just OK, nothing to write home about.

Famous for their egg tarts and pineapple bread, this is a popular cafe/bakery near Saikung's promenade. Be warned; there's normally a queue. 

Order, pick up inside and find a place to sit outside. There is also a takeaway option. 

Rich assortment of drinks, pastries and other baked items. 

Cappuccino and hot cheese and ham pastie came to HK$53.

Their pineapple bun and Portuguese egg tart are umissable. Simply delicious when fresh out of the oven. A popular way to eat pineapple bun is to sandwich a slab of butter within it which turns 菠蘿包 to 菠蘿油. I never tried but apparently it's quite tasty.

This place always has a line, but it does move really quickly. The pineapple bun is the best one I have had in Hong Kong and I highly recommend. 

The Portuguese egg tart is also really popular but I have had better and is not worth waiting for this item.  They do serve some food items, hk cafe style drinks, and other bread items. If you are in the area and are willing to wait for 20-30 minutes then this a place to visit.

At HKD11 per pineapple bun, I cannot recommend it.  I still prefer the buns at Kam Wah on Bute St in Mongkok, where the buns are always fresh out of the oven and cost only HKD6 each.  Lower price and better taste at Kam Wah.

reviews.text: 麵包老店👍🏼👍🏼菠蘿包新鮮熱辣👍🏼

差！差！差！
大家咪中伏！
以後唔会再去！
菠蘿包凍，唔新鮮，跟出面無分別
花老闆娘態度差，座呢度又唔得，果度又唔可以，又巴巴閉話要等位，等她安排先好坐，而家咩高級餐廳呀？
咖咖啡細細杯得兩啖收三十幾蚊，完全係垃圾！去 Starbucks 好飲、大杯、環境、質素好100倍！
坐低叫我試吓菠蘿包，點之外面排隊的就賣出爐包！堂食就比個隔夜唔趣仲要林哂嘅菠蘿包！真係火起！食成一佰蚊野竟然無樣得！等執笠啦！
各類麫包都即日制造，價錢貴少許，可一試。早餐可自選不同種類麫包一個及通粉包奶茶咖啡，但湯底不夠熱，可能客量多而人手只得两個關係，收銀樓面清潔煑餐冲茶一脚踼，起餐算快，可接受。
麵包新鮮又特色 味道亦不錯 尤其菠蘿包更是不可錯過再加上ㄧ片牛油絕對不能放過 ! 若加埋ㄧ杯咖啡座下來慢慢品嚐 ! 来到這𥚃必試 ! 要提示ㄧ吓有機會要排隊等候 ! 價錢係可接受的 !

Freshly baked pineapple bun! Must try when you stop by Sai Kung next time. 實在太好味!
新鮮熱辣辣，脆卜卜嘅菠蘿皮，仲有軟棉棉嘅麵包! Perfect match with their coffee.
Their egg tarts are pretty good too!
